# Styling Conventions

## Tailwind
- Use Tailwind utility classes; avoid inline styles except for dynamic values (e.g., transform)
- Add custom keyframes in `tailwind.config.ts`; add animations in `theme.extend.animation`
- Use `animation-delay-*` utilities from `globals.css` for staggered animations

## Semantic Colors
- `bg-background`, `text-foreground` - main surfaces
- `text-muted-foreground` - secondary text
- `text-foreground/80`, `text-foreground/85` - brighter body text
- `bg-primary`, `text-primary` - accents
- `border-border` - borders

